data.name: DefHelp.Text
data.value:
Windows will ask you what application would you like to use when opening a link. Choose Internet Explorer and tick an option "Always use this application". You can try that with links at the bottom of this window.
If Windows automatically resets the default browser to Edge, click "Refresh" and try setting Internet Explorer as default web browser again.
In order to get Internet Explorer working properly, you should disable BHO in "Browser Control" tab.
This feature is for Windows 10 versions before 21H2 only.
